Achievements.Name: Medal of Meritorious Service
Achievements.Description: Awarded for a long service (30 duties)

Achievements.Name: Medal of Valor
Achievements.Description: Awarded for finishing 3 duties in a row without any death or major mistakes(more than -3 reputation)

Achievements.Name: Community Policing Medal
Achievements.Description: Awarded for gaining 100 reputation points in one duty

Achievements.Name: Lifesaving Medal
Achievements.Description: Awarded for saving life by giving proper first aid instructions

Achievements.Name: Safe Driving Medal
Achievements.Description: Awarded for keeping the roads safe (Resolve 50 driving reports)

Achievements.Name: Tactical Squad Service Medal
Achievements.Description: Awarded for special tactical skills (gather 3 police teams before shooting starts)

Achievements.Name: Advanced Certification Medal
Achievements.Description: Awarded for reaching high experience level (any team member)

Achievements.Name: Order of Smile
Achievements.Description: Awarded for a sense of humor ;)

Achievements.Name: Exemplary Medical Service Medal
Achievements.Description: Awarded for saving 50 people by driving them to hospital.

Achievements.Name: Exemplary Fire Service Medal
Achievements.Description: Awarded for resolving 50 fire or technical cases.

Achievements.Name: Purple Heart
Achievements.Description: Awarded to those wounded or killed while serving

Achievements.Name: Sacrifice Medal
Achievements.Description: Awarded for resolving a case despite death of your team member
